Subject: [PATCH 0102/1383] arm64/ls1043a: create .its for RDB board

Signed-off-by: Mingkai Hu <Mingkai.Hu@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Mingkai Hu <mingkai.hu@nxp.com>
